Your brand voice is missing. Here’s how to get it back.

You’re up against a deadline and the AI gives you something that doesn’t sound like your company at all. It’s generic. You start wondering if AI can even help when it really counts.

Here’s a better way: show the AI what you want. Don’t just tell it. Give it a few real examples of how your brand writes. This is called few-shot learning. The AI will pick up on your style and match it. (1/2)
